    <item>
      <title>唐纳德·特朗普有办法在第二任期内解雇强大的金融监管机构</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/trump-has-tools-to-fire-powerful-consumer-financial-regulator-in-second-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗希特·乔普拉 (Rohit Chopra) 对非法收回汽车、取消抵押品赎回权和银行透支费用的严厉打击，使他成为消费者群体心目中的英雄和放贷者的敌人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/trump-has-tools-to-fire-powerful-consumer-financial-regulator-in-second-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 18:08:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民主党在第二次输给特朗普后再次审视自己的命运</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/democrats-again-examine-their-fate-after-second-loss-to-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普即将重返白宫，实现政治复出。在副总统卡马拉·哈里斯落败后，这一现实迫使民主党及其进步派和温和派再次重新评估其未来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/democrats-again-examine-their-fate-after-second-loss-to-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 18:00:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普赢得密歇根州</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/trump-wins-state-of-michigan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据美联社报道，共和党人唐纳德·特朗普赢得了密歇根州这个战场州及其15张选举人票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/trump-wins-state-of-michigan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 17:56:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Polymarket 的法国鲸鱼赢得 4800 万美元特朗普大奖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/polymarket-s-french-whale-hits-48-million-us-election-jackpot-with-trump-s-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[许多参与加密货币市场的人士周三都有理由为唐纳德·特朗普的胜利而洋洋得意，但一位备受关注的法国交易员的赌注将为选举结果带来数百万美元的回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/polymarket-s-french-whale-hits-48-million-us-election-jackpot-with-trump-s-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 17:50:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大选刺激美元飙升，加剧特朗普的货币问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/dollar-s-election-fueled-surge-worsens-trump-s-currency-problem</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普在大选中获胜后美元能否持续走强，取决于他重返白宫后会兑现哪些竞选承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/dollar-s-election-fueled-surge-worsens-trump-s-currency-problem</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 17:37:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥股市抛售潮消退，Sheinbaum 呼吁保持冷静，与 Larry Fink 会面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/sheinbaum-calls-for-calm-mexican-selloff-fades-after-us-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最大贸易伙伴和南方邻国的总统表示，墨西哥人应该在唐纳德·特朗普获得决定性选举胜利后保持冷静，在当地市场开始从最初的震惊中恢复之际，这听起来有点务实。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/sheinbaum-calls-for-calm-mexican-selloff-fades-after-us-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 17:14:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者如何应对特朗普的胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/wall-street-reacts-it-s-full-risk-on-as-trump-scores-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，随着唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 赢得美国总统第二任期，在与副总统卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 的势均力敌的角逐中，冒险狂潮席卷金融资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/wall-street-reacts-it-s-full-risk-on-as-trump-scores-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 14:12:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普重返白宫后民粹主义被释放</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-11-06/trump-2024-election-win-how-populist-politics-won-the-white-house</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这场决定性的胜利表明特朗普的第一任期并非偶然。现在，他已经完全掌握了白宫的行政权力，并拥有更多的自由来随心所欲地治理国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-11-06/trump-2024-election-win-how-populist-politics-won-the-white-house</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 11:30:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党接近三连胜，民主党赢得美国众议院的希望逐渐渺茫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/us-house-is-democrats-best-hope-in-brutal-election-for-party</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民主党通过控制美国众议院对唐纳德·特朗普进行强有力制衡的希望正在逐渐消退，而共和党则越来越有信心，他们将在明年围绕减税和支出的大战之前在华盛顿保持统一控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/us-house-is-democrats-best-hope-in-brutal-election-for-party</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 08:43:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
